                        <p>At request German Ambassador support protest German Consul, Guadalajara,
                            against imposition Jalisco State Government upon <pb facs="1110" n="994" xml:id="pg_994"/> German colony, including Guillermo Collignen &amp;
                            Co., extraordinary tax 150,000 pesos.</p>
